trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: 表示允许用户选择一种类型的对话框。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.

> [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]此类提示用户浏览 Windows Workflow Foundation 和.NET Framework 命名空间和及其包含的类型的列表并选择一个类型。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref> class by using an <xref:System.IServiceProvider>, an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider"></xref>, and a string.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示类型浏览器对话框是否处于设计模式。

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A> always returns `true`.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref> is in design mode; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果<xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref>处于设计模式; 否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 默认值是<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: 检索指定类型的服务对象。

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: 如果`serviceType`属于类型<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>，<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>返回服务对象。</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a null reference (`Nothing`).
The <xref:System.Type> of service object to retrieve.
A service object of type serviceType, or a null reference ( in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type serviceType.
trans-unit.target: 类型的服务对象 serviceType ，则为空引用 ( 在 Visual Basic 中) 类型的服务对象是否 serviceType 。
